00:14:07.222 --> 00:14:09.683 position:50% align:center
My daughter has been
watching you with interest.

00:14:09.766 --> 00:14:11.851 position:50% align:center
I'm flattered, ma'am.

00:14:13.895 --> 00:14:16.564 position:50% align:center
