my kind of hors d'oeuvres.

00:15:27.344 --> 00:15:29.387 position:50% align:center
Care to join me and
the girls for a drink?

00:15:29.471 --> 00:15:30.597 position:50% align:center
I'd rather not, thanks.

00:15:30.680 --> 00:15:32.849 position:50% align:center
[FURITSUKE]
Aw, aren't you precious?

00:15:37.270 --> 00:15:38.855 position:50% align:center
