I could miss it, right?

00:16:12.430 --> 00:16:13.765 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Uh...

00:16:13.848 --> 00:16:15.433 position:50% align:center
Well, thank you.

00:16:15.517 --> 00:16:16.309 position:50% align:center
[phone ringing]

00:16:16.393 --> 00:16:19.562 position:50% align:center
