00:20:48.915 --> 00:20:52.043 position:50% align:center
Introducing the
Kotori- <i>san</i> bodysuit!

00:20:52.127 --> 00:20:55.380 position:50% align:center
It even comes with his
iconic baguette!

00:20:55.463 --> 00:20:57.382 position:50% align:center
This little bird isn't
something we scraped off

00:20:57.465 --> 00:20:59.968 position:50% align:center
the cutting room floor
after the planning meeting.

00:21:00.051 --> 00:21:01.636 position:50% align:center
And it certainly wasn't
a product sample

00:21:01.720 --> 00:21:02.887 position:50% align:center
that we ordered in a haze

00:21:02.971 --> 00:21:04.556 position:50% align:center
while plowing through
a late night at work!

00:21:04.639 --> 00:21:07.183 position:50% align:center
This is a real prize
we're giving you!

00:21:07.267 --> 00:21:10.812 position:50% align:center
[EDEI]
Okay then, next number!

00:21:10.895 --> 00:21:15.900 position:50% align:center
There it is! Twenty-three!
Number twenty-three is up folks!

00:21:15.984 --> 00:21:17.861 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
Bingo!

00:21:17.944 --> 00:21:20.697 position:50% align:center
Do you not see this? You've got
three bingos, Uramichi!

00:21:20.780 --> 00:21:22.615 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
No, I don't. Shut up.

00:21:22.699 --> 00:21:24.534 position:50% align:center
The bingo gods have
spoken, Uramichi.

00:21:24.617 --> 00:21:25.744 position:50% align:center
You can't fight 'em!

00:21:25.827 --> 00:21:27.662 position:50% align:center
Just watch me.

00:21:27.746 --> 00:21:30.790 position:50% align:center
Wow, Uramichi Oniisan,
you're our winner!

00:21:30.874 --> 00:21:33.084 position:50% align:center
Hurry up and claim your prize!

00:21:33.168 --> 00:21:35.462 position:50% align:center
Wait, when did you
get behind me like that?

00:21:35.545 --> 00:21:37.964 position:50% align:center
I hope you'll take
good care of it, bud!

00:21:38.048 --> 00:21:39.966 position:50% align:center
I... don't want it.

00:21:40.050 --> 00:21:42.844 position:50% align:center
Not... my problem.

00:21:48.641 --> 00:21:51.853 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA] So, if you could've
gotten a real prize,

00:21:51.936 --> 00:21:53.855 position:50% align:center
what would you have picked?

00:21:54.856 --> 00:21:56.441 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI sighs]

00:21:56.524 --> 00:21:59.194 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
The shiitake growing kit.

00:21:59.277 --> 00:22:00.779 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
Checks out.

00:23:35.915 --> 00:23:40.920 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:23:49.304 --> 00:23:51.848 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
I'm just gonna go buy one.